<section id="course_description">
<p>ITLS teaches a comprehensive framework for rapid assessment, and appropriate interventions for critical trauma patients. The ITLS approach represents a global standard that can be applied to any situation and any environment.</p>
<p>Our ITLS course is led by experienced ALS providers with years of field experience. The course combines didactic instruction with small group training in both isolated skills and effective assessment techniques.</p>
<p>Upon completion of this course you will be able to utilize your knowledge of traumatic mechanisms and pathologies in order to initiate critical patient interventions in a timely manner.</p>
<p>Please read through our <a href="/school/policies/ceu.php">Continuing Education Policies</a> before registering.</p>
</section>
